article.description: — Rudi Williams had 24 points as Coastal Carolina topped Florida Gulf Coast 84-68 in the second round of The Basketball Classic on Monday night.
article.headline: Coastal Carolina beats FGCU 84-68 in The Basketball Classic
article.linkText: Coastal Carolina beats FGCU 84-68 in The Basketball Classic
article.story: CONWAY, S.C. -- — Rudi Williams had 24 points as Coastal Carolina topped Florida Gulf Coast 84-68 in the second round of The Basketball Classic on Monday night. Essam Mostafa added 23 points, Vince Cole had 15 points and Ebrima Dibba 10 for Coastal Carolina (18-13). Tavian Dunn-Martin had 17 points for the Eagles (22-12). Zach Anderson added 15 points and Caleb Catto had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
